---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Maxi - Frontend Engineer turned Founder">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    I'm Maxi. I'm an Argentinian 🇦🇷, and currently living in the Netherlands 🇳🇱.
  </p>
  <div class="image-wrapper">
    <img src="/images/posts/maxi-2025.jpg" alt="Maxi" class="about-img" width="400" height="400" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
  </div>

  <h2>What is this blog about?</h2>
  <p>
    I started my career as a fullstack engineer but quickly gravitated towards building interfaces, because I'm utterly curious about the psychology of what makes websites appealing and useful. Over the years I spent significant time thinking about what makes digital products succeed, with the quiet ambition of pouring all of that knowledge into products of my own.
  </p>
  <p>
    I'm also a founder of many failed projects. Throughout the last 10 years I've attempted several times to create something that sticks. In the process I learned a lot about what kills products, and slowly, a couple of things started mildly working. Mostly because of the great partners I work with.
  </p>
  <p>
    This blog follows my transition from IC to founder, in the middle of the most disruptive moment our industry has seen. I write about what I'm building, what's failing, what AI tooling actually feels like from the inside, and the honest version of what it takes to make the leap.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you're a frontend engineer sitting on ideas and wondering if this is your moment too, you're in the right place.
  </p>

  <h2>Want to talk?</h2>
  <p>I have a 100% reply ratio if you want to know more.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/neomaxzero/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.github.com/neomaxzero/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:maxicespedes7@hotmail.com">maxicespedes7@hotmail.com</a></li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .image-wrapper {
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    width: 70%;
  }
  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .image-wrapper {
      width: 35%;
    }
  }
  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  a {
    color: var(--color-primary-over-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>